        {
            "title": "添麥菲查洛美現身柏林影展   零度穿背心行紅地毯   對爭奧斯卡影帝充滿信心 : 感覺光明",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"添麥菲查洛美（Timothee Chalamet）扮演歌手卜戴倫（Bob Dylan）主演的傳記片《搖滾詩人：未知的傳奇》昨日在柏林影展作特別展映並舉行首映。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/734754501568f0a77ef344fc6d4ee097/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250215/_2025021516471623242.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">添麥菲查洛美（Timothee Chalamet）扮演歌手卜戴倫（Bob Dylan）主演的傳記片《搖滾詩人：未知的傳奇》昨日在柏林影展作特別展映並舉行首映。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>美法型男添麥菲查洛美（Timothee Chalamet）扮演歌手卜戴倫（Bob Dylan）主演的傳記片《搖滾詩人：未知的傳奇》昨日在柏林影展作特別展映並舉行首映，添麥菲在柏林的零度氣溫下穿上單薄的全身粉紅色裝束，在紅地毯上更脫去外套，只穿上背心晒麒麟臂，睇見都覺凍。\n\n</p><h2>女友Kylie Jenner摸面打氣</h2>\n<p>添麥菲被問到憑該片入圍爭奧斯卡影帝的感受，他回應稱：「感覺很光明。」在首映後，觀眾反應熱烈，不斷鼓掌，令他有點尷尬，他拖實身旁的女友Kylie Jenner，Kylie又摸他的面為他打氣。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"柏林下着雪，但添麥菲只穿背心行首映紅地毯。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c50cf34933cf3cb602934b3769c8634b/2025-02/WhatsApp_2025-02-1514_46_10_6ed354e4.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        柏林下着雪，但添麥菲只穿背心行首映紅地毯。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"添麥菲以全身粉紅色裝束示人\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/89c11eab6b97a75c14bd20190a05e631/2025-02/WhatsApp_2025-02-1514_46_11_772dca05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        添麥菲以全身粉紅色裝束示人\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"添麥菲在紅地毯逗留良久為fans簽名\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7f13174cc8d76b7bc6a07bbfe32b57be/2025-02/WhatsApp_2025-02-1514_46_12_a3cf1800.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        添麥菲在紅地毯逗留良久為fans簽名\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"添麥菲女友Kylie Jenner都陪伴他到柏林影展\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/982a9196419a9e191027bf717b0ed96e/2025-02/WhatsApp_2025-02-1514_46_12_bef6abf8.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        添麥菲女友Kylie Jenner都陪伴他到柏林影展\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"添麥菲女友Kylie Jenner都陪伴他到柏林影展\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e3eccd2ee03d71c493ef545bcc5c4618/2025-02/WhatsApp_2025-02-1514_46_12_ee4411b5.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        添麥菲女友Kylie Jenner都陪伴他到柏林影展\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"姚晨（左二）監製的主競賽片《生息之地》昨亦在柏林舉行首映。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/629f1e6f3829b82d780018bcc38112cb/2025-02/WhatsApp_2025-02-1514_46_13_52f015a6.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        姚晨（左二）監製的主競賽片《生息之地》昨亦在柏林舉行首映。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"《生息之地》導演霍猛亦亮相記者會。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/701f9876dbb8cbcb2f3a3f94b3cf5a57/2025-02/WhatsApp_2025-02-1514_46_13_53fd2be3.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        《生息之地》導演霍猛亦亮相記者會。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"姚晨監製的主競賽片《生息之地》昨亦在柏林舉行首映。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cc35948062f865fd5f854336a6ed4c35/2025-02/WhatsApp_2025-02-1514_46_15_7399bc68.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        姚晨監製的主競賽片《生息之地》昨亦在柏林舉行首映。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"添麥菲在記招則以「大黃蜂」裝扮示人。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1cbb6011aa9a7612caf2487269d2ecfe/2025-02/WhatsApp_2025-02-1514_48_04_799e8e7f.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        添麥菲在記招則以「大黃蜂」裝扮示人。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"添麥菲在記招終穿回厚衣服\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9334f350d37d903abeeda9a9ce9108aa/2025-02/WhatsApp_2025-02-1514_48_05_9c0010a9.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        添麥菲在記招終穿回厚衣服\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Emma Mackey（右）主演的《Hot Milk》都在柏林舉行記招及首映，電影大獲好評。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/30e3adcaa42b41792bd423b5208ad57f/2025-02/WhatsApp_2025-02-1514_48_06_2e0d1a05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Emma Mackey（右）主演的《Hot Milk》都在柏林舉行記招及首映，電影大獲好評。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>《生息之地》柏林首映</h2>\n<p>另外，《Hot Milk》昨日亦在柏林舉行首映禮，主演的Vicky Krieps、Fiona Shaw、《性愛自修室》Emma Mackey及導演Rebecca Lenkiewicz等亮相。入圍主競賽的內地片《生息之地》都在柏林首映，電影總製片人蔣浩、導演霍猛、監制姚晨、主演汪尚、張楚文等現身。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
